data.title: Trevor Noah: Off The Record Tour
data.meta_description: Trevor Noah is one of the most successful and multi-faceted comedians in the world.
data.text: Trevor Noah is one of the most successful and multi-faceted comedians in the world. He was the host of the Emmy® Award-winning “The Daily Show” on Comedy Central for seven years, has written, produced, and starred in 12 comedy specials, author of the #1 New York Times bestseller “Born a Crime: Stories from a South African Childhood” and currently hosts an original Spotify weekly podcast titled What Now? With Trevor Noah. In this new podcast, listeners will get a chance to hear Trevor Noah like never before. Trevor’s success has also spanned to sold out stand-up comedy shows over 5 continents. His current “Off The Record” World Tour will make a stop at Casino Rama Resort on August 24.
